{"title":"落雪的时候","authors":["肖峰"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":12,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"落雪的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肖峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落雪的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白色呈纷纷扬扬的形状"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"覆盖大地上的一切静物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界的纯洁和美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"令人神往"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落雪的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑色的煤炭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从掌子面上一直流到煤场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一条奔流的大河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在北方的土地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一片雪白的背景上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以其独特的颜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇集成河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汹涌成海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渲染出矿山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮丽的景观"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落雪的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有无数名矿工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在白与黑的颜色里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们崇尚洁白无瑕的品质"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们热爱红红火火的劳动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪与煤的交汇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展示出当代矿工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与众不同的人生"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}